Description of problem: Open Krita. It was over, last session in Krita it was go to swap. So memory going to swap.. and I need to clean up current memory, so I've trying just reload Krita. Then swap was 800~ mb. It's stack on it and not going back to 0 for some reason.(System monitor). And then close Krita, open it again and it's crash. I'm using last stable version of Krita from appimage - package from krita.org.
